insert  into `licenses`(`id_licence`,`client_id`,`status`,`license_types_id`,`date_from`,`date_to`,`welcome_ms`,`criteria`,`banner`,`bg_image`,`color_bg`,`name`,`subdomain`,`program_from`,`program_to`,`points`,`last_step`,`registration_page`,`invitation_code`,`registration_msg`,`welcome_edm`,`welcome_edm_title`,`welcome_edm_from`,`banner_edm`,`lunch_date`,`lunch_by`,`use_banner`,`invitation_edm_title`,`invitation_edm_text`,`registration_limit_date`,`max_participants`,`program_admin_email`,`freight_to`,`jobnumber`,`porcentage_rewards`) values (1,5,6,1,'08-08-2014','22-08-2014','<p><strong>Better camera, more features</strong></p>\r\n<p>We now have a probable release date for the iPhone 6 and it isn\'t far off; 9 September seems to be the anointed&nbsp;day, but what can we expect from Apple\'s flagship device?</p>\r\n<p>Here is a brief rundown of the features everyone is talking about.</p>\r\n<p>The last new iPhone, the 5s, was a revamp of the previous model, but this model will be something different altogether.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bigger</strong></p>\r\n<p>The rumours are that the new iPhone will come in two sizes: a 4.7-inch model and a larger 5.5 inch device. Both are larger than the four-inch screen on the 5s. <a href=\"http://www.techradar.com/news/phone-and-communications/mobile-phones/iphone-6-release-date-news-and-rumours-1099865\">According to Tech Radar</a>&nbsp;there may be some problems with the production of the larger model and it is not clear if both handsets will hit the shelves in tandem.</p>\r\n<p>There has even been talk of three sizes, with a cheaper iPhone 5c upgrade added to the party.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Better camera, more features</strong></p>\r\n<p>There are indications that Apple is going big with its camera this time, perhaps adding a 13-mega-pixel sensor which is smaller and clearer. This is far from clear and it may be possible that the iPhone 6 has only slightly more pixels but a better quality camera. The new operating system, iOS8, is brimming with photo editing options.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There are a few intriguing patents that people like to speculate about and Tech Radar says that wireless charging remains a possibility. It isn\'t holding its breath though.</p>\r\n<p>Perhaps most excitingly <a href=\"http://www.idownloadblog.com/2012/12/10/iphone-5s-june-2013/\">some sites are reporting</a> Apple will add near-field communication (NFC)&nbsp;to the iPhone 6, allowing for contactless payments and maybe Oyster-like travel.&nbsp;</p>','<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 60px 1px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #0c3d5d; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Program Period</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 60px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #252525; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Program From dd/mm/yy to dd/mm/yy.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 60px 1px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #0c3d5d; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Eligibility</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 60px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #252525; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">This incentive program is open for all Sales Consultants Participants of this incentive program must achieve the following criteria in order to receive a reward.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;\" />To earn a reward you must:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 78px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: circle;\">Achieve 100% of your target</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: circle;\">Achieve a minimum of 20 units of this specific product</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; line-height: 24px; list-style-type: circle;\">Complete the training provided during this year</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px 60px; line-height: 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #252525; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Everybody that completes the above criteria will receive a reward</p>','bn-1-5.jpg','Apple-Prods.png','#cacaca','Iphone 6','iphone6','08-08-2014','21-08-2014',2,5,0,'COD51','Please register to get the iphone messages. ','<p>Hey,</p>\r\n<p>Register for this program to get the iphone 6</p>','Iphone 6 Program','admin@ad-inc.com.au','edm-1-5.jpg','2014-08-08 01:08:52',27,1,'Iphone 6 invitaion','<p>Hello</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You are invited to join iphone 6 program</p>','20-08-2014',1000,NULL,0,0,10),(2,2,6,1,'08-08-2014','31-08-2014','<div class=\"container-narrow\">\r\n<div id=\"content_load\" class=\"content\">\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18pt; color: #3366ff;\">\"All our dreams come true, if we have the courage to pursue them\"<em> Walt Disney</em></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">The \"Think New\" Incentive program will take the top 23 dealerships to the City of Angels where they attend a customised training at the world renowned Disney Institute.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">Recognised for providing outstanding corporate solutions that inspire, innovate and create lasting change - the Disney Institute will provide the tools to take your dealership to the next level.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">The 5-day Toyota Disney Institute Study Tour includes:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">Return flights to Los Angeles</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">4 nights accommodation</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">All meals</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">3 days of customised training and strategic planning at the world renowned Disney Institute</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;So, keep those numbers up and good luck.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;\">The Think New Disney Institute Incentive will provide the attendees with three days of Customised training and strategic planning at the Disney Institute in Los Angeles. Study Tour duration is 5 days and 4 nights.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica;\">Eligibility</span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica;\">All current authorised Toyota Dealerships.</span></p>\r\n<h3>Participants</h3>\r\n<p>All current Sales Society/Network Central Registered Dealership Managers.</p>\r\n<h3>Minimum Qualification Criteria</h3>\r\n<p>A Dealership must RDR a minimum of 15 Total Nett units and a minimum of 5 Nett LM Sales units over the program period.</p>\r\n<h3>Criteria</h3>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://utility.adincentives.com.au/disney/staging/images/criteria-table.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"136\" /></p>\r\n<h3>Winning Criteria</h3>\r\n<p>Top 23 Dealerships, based on Dealers achieving 100% or greater of their LM Nett target over the program period AND then ranked according to Total Nett target achievement over program period by Weight &amp; Region.</p>','bn-2-2.png','bright-squares.png','#191719','Think New 2','test2','09-08-2014','31-08-2014',3,2,1,'COD22','The \"Think New\" Incentive program will take the top 23 dealerships to the City of Angels where they attend a customised training at the world renowned Disney Institute.\r\n\r\na change','<p>Toyota For Life is now a reality with everyone throughout the Toyota network thinking and talking about it.</p>\r\n<p>To align with this we are excited to launch the &ldquo;Think New 2 &ndash; Disney Institute Program&rdquo; - a Dealership incentive that rewards the 23 top achieving Dealerships with a place at the Disney Institute&rsquo;s customised training program in Los Angeles.</p>\r\n<p>This incentive program runs from 1st August &ndash; 30th September 2014 and is aligned with the Toyota For Life developments. For the first time, target achievement<strong> will not </strong>be a criteria to determine the 23 Dealership places. Instead, we will trial new KPIs that are balanced between market performance, Customer Satisfaction and Toyota&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The 23 Dealership places will be highly sought after and to secure one of these places you need to ensure your team is aware and focused on the new criteria. This will set you up for success not just in this program but also for the future.</p>\r\n<p>With the Franchise of the Future vision now a focus for all, this is the perfect time to ensure your Dealership is aligned and ready to take the next step towards achieving even greater success.</p>\r\n<p>We wish you all the best in this program and hope to see you at the Disney Institute.</p>','Think New 2 Title','admin@ad-inc.com.au','edm-2-2.png','2014-08-08 01:08:52',28,1,'Invitation title','<p>Toyota For Life is now a reality with everyone throughout the Toyota network thinking and talking about it.</p>\r\n<p>To align with this we are excited to launch the &ldquo;Think New 2 &ndash; Disney Institute Program&rdquo; - a Dealership incentive that rewards the 23 top achieving Dealerships with a place at the Disney Institute&rsquo;s customised training program in Los Angeles.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"/public/client/program/setup/licence/disney.motive8dev.adincentives.com.au\">disney.motive8dev.adincentives.com.au</a></p>\r\n<p>This incentive program runs from 1st August &ndash; 30th September 2014 and is aligned with the Toyota For Life developments. For the first time, target achievement<strong> will not </strong>be a criteria to determine the 23 Dealership places. Instead, we will trial new KPIs that are balanced between market performance, Customer Satisfaction and Toyota&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The 23 Dealership places will be highly sought after and to secure one of these places you need to ensure your team is aware and focused on the new criteria. This will set you up for success not just in this program but also for the future.</p>\r\n<p>With the Franchise of the Future vision now a focus for all, this is the perfect time to ensure your Dealership is aligned and ready to take the next step towards achieving even greater success.</p>\r\n<p>We wish you all the best in this program and hope to see you at the Disney Institute.</p>','31-08-2014',9,'admin@admin.com.au',0,0,10),(3,2,5,1,'12-08-2014','31-08-2014',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'My incentive program','new',NULL,NULL,1,2,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,NULL,0,0,10),(4,6,6,1,'19-08-2014','31-12-2014','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #99cc00; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>10 ways to improve your performance at work</strong> </span><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Successful professionals create value by finding a need and meeting it. They are unique in being able to create new products, services, business models, or just simply more effective solutions with passion and insight.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Here<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bayt.com</a>&nbsp;offers some tips on how to improve your productivity at work:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1. Plan and prioritize.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Failing to plan is planning to fail. Have an end goal in mind and organize a game plan to get there. Create a daily schedule and stick to it. Be punctual and don&rsquo;t postpone. Determine what projects and tasks are critical, urgent and create the largest value and benefit to the business. Select what you can easily postpone and what you can delegate without hurting results; a lion&rsquo;s chunk of prioritizing involves simply learning to say no.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://blog.bayt.com/2013/01/easily-distracted-5-ways-to-reduce-online-distraction-at-work/\" target=\"_blank\">Avoid distractions</a>.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Focus is a key trait of productive professionals; distractions are the bane of productivity. According to Bayt.com&rsquo;s &lsquo;Rest and Recreation Habits Among MENA Professionals&rsquo; poll earlier this year,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://blog.bayt.com/2013/01/infographic-rest-and-recreation-habits-among-mena-professionals/\" target=\"_blank\">30.7%<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></a>of respondents say that they spend more than five hours a day surfing the internet just for fun. Don&rsquo;t lose sight of your vision, mission and values along your journey. Remember, sustainable success is rarely about revolutionary breakthroughs, it&rsquo;s invariably a process of evolution that feeds off consistent progress.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. Set interim milestones and reward yourself.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The road to your destination may be long and winding; the end-goal may still be a few moons away. But don&rsquo;t let that stop you from taking time to smell the roses. Set clear milestones for interim success and reward yourself with a break from time to time. Breaking a long project into chunks of mini-tasks with individual milestones and success metrics will keep your morale high and energy levels soaring.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/en/press-release-article-11884/\" target=\"_blank\">62.2%<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></a>of professionals in the region polled by Bayt.com claim that they do receive recognition or praise at work but only from others; make sure to tabulate your own progress and reward yourself too!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Read something new.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Try to allocate some time every day to read, refine skills and<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://blog.bayt.com/2012/06/twelve-ways-to-be-a-lifelong-learner/\" target=\"_blank\">learn something new</a>.&nbsp; Take notes and share your knowledge whenever possible; in this way you are learning more actively and also building a reputation and establishing expertise for yourself. With change happening all around you, the quickest way to increase productivity, improve performance, and maintain a competitive edge is to stay fully abreast of the latest tools, trends, and technologies in your industry.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" title=\"blocked::http://www.bayt.com/en/poll-results/?poll_id=20750\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/en/poll-results/?poll_id=20750\" target=\"_blank\">77.9%<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></a>of respondents to a Bayt.com poll indicated they read constantly and<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" title=\"blocked::http://www.bayt.com/en/poll-results/?poll_id=20700\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/en/poll-results/?poll_id=20700\" target=\"_blank\">69.6%</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>indicated they believe reading is vital to career progress.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. Ask a question.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">What if I did this differently? What if there is a faster, easier, more effective way to achieve the same results? What if I changed my pitch/tone/content/brand or message? Whatever the question you ask, you need to constantly challenge the status quo and question yourself and others to find out whether you are really working as productively as you possibly could. Never be satisfied that things can&rsquo;t be improved.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. Simply listen.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Whether within your team or to outside clients, you need to listen regularly and often. They will provide you with first-hand insights into your performance and alert you to their preferences so you can better meet demand. You may be able to amplify your productivity substantially by better understanding and honing in on actual consumer expectations and learning to anticipate their needs. Listen to your team, your stakeholders and your peers in the industry too.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">7. Take stock of your competitive space.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Rarely&nbsp; are we blessed with a space void of competitors; understanding your market is essential. Observe what your competitors are up to, analyze what they are doing right &ndash; and not so right &ndash; and treat their experience as a key learning opportunity to keep innovating and iterating.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">8. Give credit where credit is due.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">All of us rely on the cooperation, input, feedback and buy-in of others to get our job done. To facilitate and magnify this kind of cooperation, you need to give credit to others and show gratitude along the way. Help those around you to excel and you&rsquo;re bound to rise together.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">9. Stay healthy.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Good health and an acceptable work-life balance lead to better productivity. A recent poll conducted by Bayt.com&nbsp;reveals that professionals in the Middle East and North Africa are keen on maintaining a healthy work-life balance. In fact,&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/en/press-release-article-14602/\" target=\"_blank\">26.9%<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></a>of polled professionals believe that their poor work-life balance has jeopardized both their mental health and happiness, and a staggering&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.bayt.com/en/press-release-article-14602/\" target=\"_blank\">64.8%<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></a>of them would even accept a pay cut to have more free time on their job.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">To sustain peak performance over the long term and avoid stress and burnout, you need to be physically and mentally healthy. Eat well, sleep sufficiently and try to squeeze some exercise into your routine on a regular basis.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">10. Put your heart in it.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Passion is one of the single most important drivers of success. If your heart and soul aren&rsquo;t in what you are doing, you are likely not putting your best effort forward. Do some soul-searching and find out what it will take to make you love what you do and perform to the very best of your abilities. Make sure your values are being reflected and respected in what you do and that you see true meaning in your work.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #99cc00;\">12 productive ways to take a break at work</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Whether writing a long report, entering hundreds of names into a database, or dealing with a tough client, sometimes it&rsquo;s nice to take a five and regroup.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">When I have writer\'s block or get stuck on a certain project, for example, sometimes I just need to get up and separate myself from the situation and revisit it in a bit with fresh eyes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">But instead of losing time stalking old friends on Facebook, it could be nice to fill a break with something, or someone, a bit more productive. Here are twelve productive ways to switch up your focus, find new inspiration, and get more energy in your down time.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1. Watch a TED video.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Covering a huge range of topics, TED Talks offer something for everyone. I\'d recommend exploring one avenue that has nothing to do with your current interests or expertise; you\'re bound to discover something you didn\'t know before.&nbsp;Usually around ten minutes, these videos are a great way to challenge what you previously thought and stay motivated to push ahead with your work. If you&rsquo;re not sure where to start, check out the list of the<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2012/09/top-20-most-watched-ted-talks\" target=\"_blank\">20 most-watched TED Talks</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>of all time or our list of<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/09/4-inspiring-tedx-videos-from-arab-entrepreneurs\" target=\"_blank\">4 TED Talks</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>from Arab entrepreneurs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2. Read an article or a new book.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">While you&rsquo;re pausing to take a break from work, take some time to see what&rsquo;s going on in the world around you. Pick a few online or mobile news sources that capture your attention or cover happenings in your field and dive in. Our team likes to use mobile news aggregators<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/02/mobile-app-nabd-offers-personalized-news-in-arabic\" target=\"_blank\">Nabd</a>,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://www.pulse.me/\" target=\"_blank\">Pulse</a>,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://news360.com/\" target=\"_blank\">News360</a>&nbsp;to see the latest news; I always like to know what others are talking about and where my field is heading. If you\'ve found a good book, read a section or chapter while you\'re taking a break; you\'ve probably already checked out Chris Schroeder\'s&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/08/must-read-startup-rising-the-entrepreneurial-revolution-remaking-the-middle-east\" target=\"_blank\">new book</a>, so here is our list of&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/02/15-must-read-books-for-middle-east-entrepreneurs\" target=\"_blank\">15 must-read books</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>for entrepreneurs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. Check out your site&rsquo;s trends.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">It&rsquo;s always fun to look back at your analytics, if you aren\'t obsessed with them already. If it\'s under your jurisdiction, check them out on platforms like<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2012/05/woopra-s-new-interface-eases-quick-decision-making\" target=\"_blank\">Woopra</a>,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.parsely.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Parse.ly</a>,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://chartbeat.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Chartbeat</a>, or&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/07/how-to-track-your-website-s-progress-on-google-analytics\" target=\"_blank\">Google trends and analytics</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>to see how you\'re progressing. If it\'s not your responsibility, but you\'re still really dedicated, it can be revealing to Google your company and see what others are saying about your work and how the company is perceived online; you may find unexpected feedback that can help you improve the brand.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Read what your followers are sharing.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Besides looking at your own company&rsquo;s activity, see what your fans are talking about on their own<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/stephanienour/2013/07/don-t-make-these-10-social-media-mistakes\" target=\"_blank\">social networks</a>. Check out what they tweet, like, and share and see if your company can meet their interests and join the conversation. Besides building your own brand, it&rsquo;s also interesting to participate in the latest conversations in your field. Like, follow, and engage with other content as well to build your reputation as an active and respected member of the community.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. Get yourself organized.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">When you\'re running around and getting things done, it\'s easy for papers to pile on your desk or workspace. If you have some time for a break, clean up your space to make it inviting for others and more conducive to helping you work through new ideas. It might be a good idea to go through unanswered e-mails to make sure you\'re not missing anything. Get rid of stuff that you don&rsquo;t need, whether on your desk, filling up your inbox, or cluttering your harddrive; don&rsquo;t be afraid to throw things out if you don&rsquo;t need them anymore.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. Question your colleagues.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Sometimes, the best resource or mentor is sitting right next you. Don&rsquo;t be afraid to step away from your desk or workspace to chat with those around you. This can be particularly effective in a<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/07/10-popular-coworking-spaces-in-the-arab-world\" target=\"_blank\">coworking space</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>when everyone is working on very different projects. For a few minutes, step away from your desk and pick your neighbor&rsquo;s brain about what they&rsquo;re working on, if they have suggestions for your project, or just to hear about their past experience. You may make a new friend or mentor, but you&rsquo;ll certainly make a friendlier colleague.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">7. Get inspired.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">There is a lot of inspiration to be found outside of your industry. Go online and check out cool designers, research local artists and their work, or even begin doodling yourself to express your own creativity. Sometimes seeing what others can create can motivate you to imagine your own innovations. Take time to check out what others are creating, whether<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/07/why-we-need-better-arts-education-in-the-arab-world\" target=\"_blank\">art</a>,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/02/can-anghami-fend-off-deezer-s-entrance-into-the-arab-music-market\" target=\"_blank\">music</a>, or tech, to find inspiration in your own work.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline;\">8. Set short-term tasks and priorities.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">When work is piling on, it&rsquo;s easy to lose track of priorities and little tasks that get thrown your way. Take some time each day to clearly outline your goals for the day and the week to begin checking off tasks, even the little ones, that otherwise could get lost in the shuffle. The best way to eat an elephant is one bite at a time, so break things down into small tasks and get them done.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline;\">9. Take an online course.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">There are plenty of courses available online that let you move at your own pace and even complete tasks in short intervals. Research online to find a new skill you are interesting in cultivating and find out if there is an<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2012/11/10-education-technology-resources-for-the-arab-world\" target=\"_blank\">educational</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>course available online to supplement your own skills.<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.codecademy.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>Codeacademy</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>for example teaches users to code for free and can be paused and returned to easily.<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://www.udacity.com/home?utm_expid=55211281-1.iRgFPz8LSRyJfApyQiAx1g.1&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.udacity.com%2Fhome\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;Udacity</a>too offers tech courses that you can complete in short intervals, and there are tons of other&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/05/what-are-moocs-what-mean-for-middle-east\" target=\"_blank\">massive open online courses</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>(MOOC) alternatives. Find a skill you&rsquo;re lacking and start fostering it in your free time &ndash; it may come in handy down the road.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline;\">10. Get healthy.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">It&rsquo;s important to stretch your legs, get the blood pumping, and&nbsp;move around rather than sitting in front of a computer screen all day. During your break, it may be worth it to head to a nearby gym to get in your daily workout; here are<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.wamda.com/2013/07/10-reasons-why-exercise-makes-you-better-at-your-job\" target=\"_blank\">10 reasons</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>why exercise makes you better at your job.&nbsp;If I need an energy boost, I like to enjoy a healthy snack, have a cup of coffee or rehydrate with a glass of water. Find ways to keep your energy up and refuel in a healthy way to stay engaged and focused throughout the day.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">11. Expand your network online.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">For some, social networking is just a distraction. But platforms like LinkedIn can have a huge personal benefit for your career. I like to check it every day just to see what people are talking about, who is meeting who, and to sustain a connection with people I recently met in person. It&rsquo;s a great way to build current relationships or find out if others are closer to you than you thought.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline;\">12. Take time to find your own creativity.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"GlensDefault\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Not every break needs to be filled with specific content however. It&rsquo;s important for your brain to rest as well;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #58bc0c; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/10/opinion/sunday/relax-youll-be-more-productive.html?pagewanted=all\" target=\"_blank\">studies have shown</a><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>that more downtime and rest can lead to greater productivity. Some even recommend taking a power nap for half an hour in the early afternoon to wake up refreshed for the rest of the day.&nbsp;Teams too can pause their work and take time to take a step back, refocus and get everyone to move forward on the same page. Each of us needs some quiet time once in a while to recharge and separate ourselves from our work, I know I do. And who knows- while reviewing the day in your mind, you may just rediscover a detail you missed or an idea worth pursuing.</span></p>','bn-4-6.png','grunge-texture.png','#E3EC62','Improve your performance','incentive','20-08-2014','31-12-2014',3,4,1,'COD64','Successful professionals create value by finding a need and meeting it. They are unique in being able to create new products, services, business models, or just simply more effective solutions with passion and insight.','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #333333;\">Successful professionals create value by finding a need and meeting it. They are unique in being able to create new products, services, business models, or just simply more effective solutions with passion and insight.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #333333;\">Failing to plan is planning to fail. Have an end goal in mind and organize a game plan to get there. Create a daily schedule and stick to it. Be punctual and don&rsquo;t postpone. Determine what projects and tasks are critical, urgent and create the largest value and benefit to the business. Select what you can easily postpone and what you can delegate without hurting results; a lion&rsquo;s chunk of prioritizing involves simply learning to say no.</span></p>','Improve your performance at work','admin@ad-inc.com.au','edm-4-6.png','2014-08-18 21:08:33',30,1,'Improve your performance at work - Invitation','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,s